{"tid":2410088,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果真係有輪迴嘅話，林鄭下世會做乜？","createTime":"2021-02-16T10:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T15:43:23.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d6b2613b31c94d83fc365ca78e55d4cac6936acb","tid":2410088,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"佢今世造嘅罪孽，會有乜嘢結果？"},{"pid":"4c5311f1cfe8c463ebdfcdf3fb83c88b92d72596","tid":2410088,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"餓修羅"},{"pid":"63f7d8630cc721d28f2932d7580296d7b5907198","tid":2410088,"uid":299263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"參考毘琉璃個故 &darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<br />\n毘琉璃王殺意堅決，已不可救。釋迦族人遭到毘琉璃王殘虐屠殺，但並沒滅絶。<br />\n<br />\n毘琉璃王後期荒淫酒色，在大河遊憩時，船隊遇暴風雨，船沈而死，從此，憍薩羅國被摩揭陀國阿闍世王吞併。佛經記載，毗琉璃王死後墮入無間地獄受苦。"},{"pid":"f54cf076866b2812008edccb73889071e3693496","tid":2410088,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"月蛾"},{"pid":"5d87687a436d3159909d806959777b853948aba9","tid":2410088,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:30:17.000Z","msg":"你個女"},{"pid":"076998a9fb552df3ca231e184ae9e221cc428990","tid":2410088,"uid":183058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>穿肋地獄</strong></span><br />\n     《玉歷》云：<strong><span class=\"red\">凡為官不忠、不廉、不恤人民</span></strong>，或逃獄、損人墳墓、毀人名譽、捏造偽證、幫人解除婚約，死後均墮此地獄。當今言論自由，已到肆無忌憚之地，毀謗或抨擊所引起的糾紛、禍害，層出不窮，危亂社會影響很大，或有專作偽證、離婚證人，破人家庭者，死後均墮穿肋之苦刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhtuArM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhtuArM.jpg&h=6874bfa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>狗嚎狼啖地獄</strong></span><br />\n   <strong><span class=\"red\">  凡滋事生端、為保權位，不忠不義、無心無肺者</span></strong>，墮此地獄。諺云：狼心狗肺，此乃形容為人險惡，無有良心者。此輩生前叱吒一時，死後被狗啃、被狼啖，一切身分段段脫落，節節骨散，果報之烈，真慘不忍睹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U8boET8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8boET8.jpg&h=ad2c2b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d884f35c63e4ee153baa611e7a66d10900942ab","tid":2410088,"uid":69866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a94f9cedad923eca206bdbe5221e1cd393e60d2","tid":2410088,"uid":337210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"佢死果陣放下屠刀 會成佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bc6d3e12112ff06e2155985f60da7f049c400b","tid":2410088,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"蛆蟲"},{"pid":"1439416e7abe3a70c8748a1421c3dcf7f468f6af","tid":2410088,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a94f9cedad923eca206bdbe5221e1cd393e60d2","tid":2410088,"uid":337210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"佢死果陣放下屠刀 會成佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"再揾個father去床邊，信埋教先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2da9937cffbdb0f14bd02a71a12d2253a3690bf","tid":2410088,"uid":103123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"信主得救<br />\n係天堂享緊福<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/